name: Bulbasaur
pokedex_description: Bulbasaur can be seen napping in bright sunlight. There is a seed on its back. By soaking up the sun's rays, the seed grows progressively larger.

name: Ivysaur
pokedex_description: To support its bulb, Ivysaur's legs grow sturdy. If it spends more time lying in the sunlight, the bud will soon bloom into a large flower.

name: Venusaur
pokedex_description: Venusaur's flower is said to take on vivid colors if it gets plenty of nutrition and sunlight. The flower's aroma soothes the emotions of people.

name: Charmander
pokedex_description: The flame that burns at the tip of its tail is an indication of its emotions. The flame wavers when Charmander is happy, and blazes when it is enraged.

name: Charmeleon
pokedex_description: Without pity, its sharp claws destroy foes. If it encounters a strong enemy, it becomes agitated, and the flame on its tail flares with a bluish white color.

name: Charizard
pokedex_description: A Charizard flies about in search of strong opponents. It breathes intense flames that can melt any material. However, it will never torch a weaker foe.

name: Squirtle
pokedex_description: Its shell is not just for protection. Its rounded shape and the grooves on its surface minimize resistance in water, enabling Squirtle to swim at high speeds.

name: Wartortle
pokedex_description: Its large tail is covered with rich, thick fur that deepens in color with age. The scratches on its shell are evidence of this Pokémon's toughness in battle.

name: Blastoise
pokedex_description: The waterspouts that protrude from its shell are highly accurate. Their bullets of water can precisely nail tin cans from a distance of over 160 feet.

name: Caterpie
pokedex_description: Tiene una cabeza y ojos muy grandes y unas antenas rojas llamativas, todo para asemejarse a un Ekans e intimidar a sus muchos depredadores.

name: Metapod
pokedex_description: Utiliza una seda especial que se endurece al contacto con el aire para crear una coraza resistente mientras espera para evolucionar de nuevo.

name: Butterfree
pokedex_description: Tiene un gran apetito y puede alejarse hasta 10km para buscar miel y almacenarla en su nido. Poliniza a muchos Pokémon planta.

name: Weedle
pokedex_description: Los aguijones de su cabeza y cola liberan veneno al mínimo roce y pueden producir desde sensación de picor o quemazón hasta nauseas.

name: Kakuna
pokedex_description: Viven en colmenas donde los Weedle se ayudan a hacerse las pupas o corazas y los Beedrill protegen al resto hasta que evolucionan.

name: Beedrill
pokedex_description: En cada colmena hay una Beedrill reina que es la que pone huevos y el resto la defiende. El más fuerte además la fecunda cuando es necesario.

name: Pidgey
pokedex_description: It has an extremely sharp sense of direction. It can unerringly return home to its nest, however far it may be removed from its familiar surroundings.

name: Pidgeotto
pokedex_description: This Pokémon flies around, patrolling its large territory. If its living space is violated, it shows no mercy in thoroughly punishing the foe with its sharp claws.

name: Pidgeot
pokedex_description: This Pokémon has gorgeous, glossy feathers. Many trainers are so captivated by the beautiful feathers on its head that they choose Pidgeot as their Pokémon.

name: Rattata
pokedex_description: A Rattata is cautious in the extreme. Even while it is asleep, it constantly moves its ears and listens for danger. It will make its nest anywhere.

name: Raticate
pokedex_description: A Raticate's sturdy fangs grow steadily. To keep them ground down, it gnaws on rocks and logs. It may even chew on the walls of houses.

name: Spearow
pokedex_description: Its loud cry can be heard over half a mile away. If its high, keening cry is heard echoing all around, it is a sign that they are warning each other of danger.

name: Fearow
pokedex_description: Its long neck and elongated beak are ideal for catching prey in soil or water. It deftly moves this extended and skinny beak to pluck prey.

name: Ekans
pokedex_description: An Ekans curls itself up in a spiral while it rests. This position allows it to quickly respond to an enemy from any direction with a threat from its upraised head.

name: Arbok
pokedex_description: This Pokémon has a terrifically strong constricting power. It can even flatten steel oil drums. Once it wraps its body around its foe, escaping is impossible.

name: Pikachu
pokedex_description: It stores electricity in the electric sacs on its cheeks. When it releases pent-up energy in a burst, the electric power is equal to a lightning bolt.

name: Raichu
pokedex_description: If it stores too much electricity, its behavior turns aggressive. To avoid this, it occasionally discharges excess energy and calms itself down.

name: Sandshrew
pokedex_description: When it curls up in a ball, it can make any attack bounce off harmlessly. Its hide has turned tough and solid as a result of living in the desert.

name: Sandslash
pokedex_description: It curls up in a ball to protect itself from enemy attacks. It also curls up to prevent heatstroke during the daytime when temperatures rise sharply.

name: Nidoran
pokedex_description: Its highly toxic barbs are thought to have developed as protection for this small-bodied Pokémon. When enraged, it releases a horrible toxin from its horn.

name: Nidorina
pokedex_description: When it is with its friends or family, its barbs are tucked away to prevent injury. It appears to become nervous if separated from the others.

name: Nidoqueen
pokedex_description: It is adept at sending foes flying with harsh tackles using its tough, scaly body. This Pokémon is at its strongest when it is defending its young.

name: Nidoran
pokedex_description: The male Nidoran has developed muscles that freely move its ears in any direction. Even the slightest sound does not escape this Pokémon's notice.

name: Nidorino
pokedex_description: Its horn is harder than a diamond. If it senses a hostile presence, all the barbs on its back bristle up at once, and it challenges the foe with all its might.

name: Nidoking
pokedex_description: A Nidoking's thick tail packs enormously destructive power capable of toppling a metal transmission tower. Once it goes on a rampage, there is no stopping it.

name: Clefairy
pokedex_description: On every night of a full moon, they come out to play. When dawn arrives, the tired Clefairy go to sleep nestled up against each other in deep and quiet mountains.

name: Clefable
pokedex_description: A Clefable uses its wings to skip lightly as if it were flying. Its bouncy step lets it even walk on water. On quiet, moonlit nights, it strolls on lakes.

name: Vulpix
pokedex_description: It can freely control fire, making fiery orbs fly like will-o'-the-wisps. Just before evolution, its six tails grow hot as if on fire.

name: Ninetales
pokedex_description: It has long been said that each of the nine tails embody an enchanted power. A long-lived Ninetales will have fur that shines like gold.

name: Jigglypuff
pokedex_description: Puede inflarse de aire hasta volúmenes increíbles para poder flotar o cantar durante un largo tiempo sin necesidad de coger aire.

name: Wigglytuff
pokedex_description: Controla muy bien su capacidad para inflarse e intimidar así a sus enemigos y propinarles golpes más dolorosos al tener un tamaño mayor.

name: Zubat
pokedex_description: While living in pitch-black caverns, their eyes gradually grew shut and deprived them of vision. They use ultrasonic waves to detect obstacles.

name: Golbat
pokedex_description: Its fangs easily puncture even thick animal hide. It loves to feast on the blood of people and Pokémon. It flits about in darkness and strikes from behind.

name: Oddish
pokedex_description: This Pokémon grows by absorbing moonlight. During the daytime, it buries itself in the ground, leaving only its leaves exposed to avoid detection by its enemies.

name: Gloom
pokedex_description: A horribly noxious honey drools from its mouth. One whiff of the honey can result in memory loss. Some fans are said to enjoy this overwhelming stink, however.

name: Vileplume
pokedex_description: In seasons when it produces more pollen, the air around a Vileplume turns yellow with the powder as it walks. The pollen is highly toxic and causes paralysis.

name: Paras
pokedex_description: A Paras has parasitic tochukaso mushrooms growing on its back. They grow by drawing nutrients from the host. They are valued as a medicine for long life.

name: Parasect
pokedex_description: Parasect are known to infest the roots of large trees en masse and drain nutrients. When an infested tree dies, they move onto another tree all at once.

name: Venonat
pokedex_description: En la naturaleza se alimenta continuamente de la madera de distintos árboles hasta los meses de primavera, momento en el que evoluciona.

name: Venomoth
pokedex_description: Es de hábitos nocturnos y se siente muy atraído por la luz. Suelen aparearse en primavera y se reproducen a principios del verano.

name: Diglett
pokedex_description: Diglett are raised in most farms. The reason is simple--wherever they burrow, the soil is left perfectly tilled for growing delicious crops.

name: Dugtrio
pokedex_description: Because the triplets originally split from one body, they think exactly alike. They work cooperatively to burrow endlessly through the ground.

name: Meowth
pokedex_description: En comparación con otros felinos es muy activo, le encanta explorar y buscar objetos brillantes. No tolera la soledad y suele vivir en grupos.

name: Persian
pokedex_description: Antiguamente era la mascota de los aristócratas ibéricos debido a su elegancia. Hacen brillar la joya de su frente para llamar la atención.

name: Psyduck
pokedex_description: When its headache intensifies, it starts using strange powers. However, it has no recollection of its powers, so it always looks befuddled and bewildered.

name: Golduck
pokedex_description: A Golduck is an adept swimmer. It sometimes joins competitive swimmers in training. It uses psychic powers when its forehead shimmers with light.

name: Mankey
pokedex_description: When it starts shaking and its nasal breathing turns rough, it's a sure sign of anger. However, since this happens instantly, there is no time to flee.

name: Primeape
pokedex_description: When it becomes furious, its blood circulation becomes more robust, and its muscles are made stronger. But it also becomes much less intelligent.

name: Growlithe
pokedex_description: Its superb sense of smell ensures that this Pokémon won't forget any scent, no matter what. It uses its sense of smell to detect the emotions of others.

name: Arcanine
pokedex_description: This fleet-footed Pokémon is said to run over 6,200 miles in a single day and night. The fire that blazes wildly within its body is its source of power.

name: Poliwag
pokedex_description: It is possible to see this Pokémon's spiral innards right through its thin skin. However, the skin is also very flexible. Even sharp fangs bounce right off it.

name: Poliwhirl
pokedex_description: Its body surface is always wet and slick with an oily fluid. Because of this greasy covering, it can easily slip and slide out of the clutches of any enemy in battle.

name: Poliwrath
pokedex_description: Its highly developed muscles never grow fatigued, however much it exercises. This Pokémon can swim back and forth across the Pacific Ocean without effort.

name: Abra
pokedex_description: A Pokémon that sleeps 18 hours a day. Observation revealed that it uses Teleport to change its location once every hour.

name: Kadabra
pokedex_description: It is rumored that a boy with psychic abilities suddenly transformed into Kadabra while he was assisting research into extrasensory powers.

name: Alakazam
pokedex_description: While it has strong psychic abilities and high intelligence, an Alakazam's muscles are very weak. It uses psychic power to move its body.

name: Machop
pokedex_description: It continually undertakes strenuous training to master all forms of martial arts. Its strength lets it easily hoist a sumo wrestler onto its shoulders.

name: Machoke
pokedex_description: A belt is worn by a Machoke to keep its overwhelming power under control. Because it is so dangerous, no one has ever removed the belt.

name: Machamp
pokedex_description: It is impossible to defend against punches and chops doled out by its four arms. Its fighting spirit flares up when it faces a tough opponent.

name: Bellsprout
pokedex_description: A Bellsprout's thin and flexible body lets it bend and sway to avoid any attack, however strong it may be. From its mouth, it leaks a fluid that melts even iron.

name: Weepinbell
pokedex_description: At night, a Weepinbell hangs on to a tree branch with its hooked rear and sleeps. If it moves around in its sleep, it may wake up to find itself on the ground.

name: Victreebel
pokedex_description: The long vine extending from its head is waved about as if it were a living thing to attract prey. When an unsuspecting victim approaches, it is swallowed whole.

name: Tentacool
pokedex_description: Its body is almost entirely composed of water. It ensnares its foe with its two long tentacles, then stabs with the poison stingers at their tips.

name: Tentacruel
pokedex_description: It lives in complex rock formations on the ocean floor and traps prey using its 80 tentacles. Its red orbs glow when it grows excited or agitated.

name: Geodude
pokedex_description: It climbs mountain paths using only the power of its arms. Because they look just like boulders lining paths, hikers may step on them without noticing.

name: Graveler
pokedex_description: They descend from mountains by tumbling down steep slopes. They are so brutal, they smash aside obstructing trees and massive boulders with thunderous tackles.

name: Golem
pokedex_description: It is said to live in volcanic craters on mountain peaks. Once a year, it sheds its hide and grows larger. The shed hide crumbles and returns to the soil.

name: Ponyta
pokedex_description: A Ponyta is very weak at birth. It can barely stand up. Its legs become stronger as it stumbles and falls while trying to keep up with its parent.

name: Rapidash
pokedex_description: It usually canters casually in the fields and plains. But once a Rapidash turns serious, its fiery manes flare and blaze as it gallops its way up to 150 mph.

name: Slowpoke
pokedex_description: It catches prey by dipping its tail in water at the side of a river. But it often forgets what it is doing and spends entire days just loafing at water's edge.

name: Slowbro
pokedex_description: Its tail has a Shellder firmly attached with a bite. As a result, the tail can't be used for fishing anymore. This forces it to reluctantly swim and catch prey.

name: Magnemite
pokedex_description: The units at its sides are extremely powerful magnets. They generate enough magnetism to draw in iron objects from over 300 feet away.

name: Magneton
pokedex_description: It is actually three Magnemite linked by magnetism. It generates powerful radio waves that raise temperatures by 3.6 degrees F within a 3,300-foot radius.

name: Farfetch'd
pokedex_description: It is always seen with a stick from a plant. Apparently, there are good sticks and bad sticks. This Pokémon occasionally fights with others over choice sticks.

name: Doduo
pokedex_description: Even while eating or sleeping, one of the heads remains always vigilant for any sign of danger. When threatened, it flees at over 60 miles per hour.

name: Dodrio
pokedex_description: A peculiar Pokémon species with three heads. It vigorously races across grassy plains even in arid seasons with little rainfall.

name: Seel
pokedex_description: Seel hunt for prey in frigid, ice-covered seas. When it needs to breathe, it punches a hole through the ice with the sharply protruding section of its head.

name: Dewgong
pokedex_description: It loves to snooze on bitterly cold ice. The sight of this Pokémon sleeping on a glacier was mistakenly thought to be a mermaid by a mariner long ago.

name: Grimer
pokedex_description: Born from polluted sludge in the sea, Grimer's favorite food is anything filthy. They feed on wastewater pumped out from factories.

name: Muk
pokedex_description: It prefers warm and humid habitats. In the summertime, the toxic substances in its body intensify, making Muk reek like putrid kitchen garbage.

name: Shellder
pokedex_description: At night, it burrows a hole in the seafloor with its broad tongue to make a place to sleep. While asleep, it closes its shell, but leaves its tongue hanging out.

name: Cloyster
pokedex_description: It swims in the sea by swallowing water, then jetting it out toward the rear. The Cloyster shoots spikes from its shell using the same system.

name: Gastly
pokedex_description: When exposed to a strong wind, a Gastly's gaseous body quickly dwindles away. They cluster under the eaves of houses to escape the ravages of wind.

name: Haunter
pokedex_description: If a Haunter beckons you while it is floating in darkness, don't approach it. This Pokémon will try to lick you with its tongue and steal your life away.

name: Gengar
pokedex_description: Deep in the night, your shadow cast by a streetlight may suddenly overtake you. It is actually a Gengar running past you, pretending to be your shadow.

name: Onix
pokedex_description: There is a magnet in its brain that prevents an Onix from losing direction while tunneling. As it grows older, its body becomes steadily rounder and smoother.

name: Drowzee
pokedex_description: If your nose becomes itchy while you are sleeping, it's a sure sign that a Drowzee is standing above your pillow and trying to eat your dream through your nostrils.

name: Hypno
pokedex_description: The arcing movement and glitter of the pendulum in a Hypno's hand lull the foe into deep hypnosis. While searching for prey, it polishes the pendulum.

name: Krabby
pokedex_description: Presenta un dimorfismo sexual claro, en el macho los surcos ventrales forman un triángulo isósceles y en la hembra un triángulo redondeado.

name: Kingler
pokedex_description: Muda su concha para crecer, si pierde su pinza grande la opuesta crece más convirtiéndose en la grande y regenera la otra que pasa a ser la pequeña.

name: Voltorb
pokedex_description: It bears an uncanny and unexplained resemblance to a Poké Ball. Because it explodes at the slightest shock, even veteran trainers treat it with caution.

name: Electrode
pokedex_description: They appear in great numbers at electric power plants. Because they feed on electricity, they cause massive and chaotic blackouts in nearby cities.

name: Exeggcute
pokedex_description: It consists of six eggs that care for each other. The eggs attract each other and spin around. When cracks increasingly appear, it is close to evolution.

name: Exeggutor
pokedex_description: Originally from the tropics, Exeggutor's heads grow larger from exposure to strong sunlight. It is said that when the heads fall, they group to form an Exeggcute.

name: Cubone
pokedex_description: Ha tenido que sobrevivir en un ecosistema inhóspito, como el desierto, desde muy pequeño sin su madre. Por ello es muy duro y autosuficiente.

name: Marowak
pokedex_description: Usan su hueso para producir sonidos golpeando rocas para avisar a otros de que están invadiendo su territorio o para impresionar a las hembras.

name: Hitmonlee
pokedex_description: Its legs freely stretch and contract. Using these springlike limbs, it bowls over foes with devastating kicks. After battle, it rubs down its tired legs.

name: Hitmonchan
pokedex_description: A Hitmonchan is said to possess the spirit of a boxer who aimed to become the world champion. Having an indomitable spirit means that it will never give up.

name: Lickitung
pokedex_description: Whenever it sees something unfamiliar, it always licks the object because it memorizes things by texture and taste. It is somewhat put off by sour things.

name: Koffing
pokedex_description: Getting up close to a Koffing will give you a chance to observe, through its thin skin, the toxic gases swirling inside. It blows up at the slightest stimulation.

name: Weezing
pokedex_description: By diluting its toxic gases with a special process, the highest grade of perfume can be extracted. To Weezing, gases emanating from garbage are the ultimate feast.

name: Rhyhorn
pokedex_description: Once it starts running, it doesn't stop. Its tiny brain makes it so stupid that it can't remember why it started running in the first place.

name: Rhydon
pokedex_description: Its horn, which rotates like a drill, destroys tall buildings with one strike. It stands on its hind legs, and its brain is well developed.

name: Chansey
pokedex_description: Chansey lay nutritionally excellent eggs every day. The eggs are so delicious, they are eagerly devoured by even those who have lost their appetite.

name: Tangela
pokedex_description: Su cuerpo está cubierto de enredaderas que lo protegen. Nadie sabe qué aspecto tiene sin ellas ya que le vuelven a crecer en segundos si se le arrancan.

name: Kangaskhan
pokedex_description: If you come across a young Kangaskhan playing by itself, never try to catch it. The baby's parent is sure to be in the area, and it will become violently enraged.

name: Horsea
pokedex_description: By cleverly flicking the fins on its back side to side, it moves in any direction while facing forward. It spits ink to escape if it senses danger.

name: Seadra
pokedex_description: The poisonous barbs all over its body are highly valued as ingredients for making traditional herbal medicine. It shows no mercy to anything approaching its nest.

name: Goldeen
pokedex_description: In the springtime, schools of Goldeen can be seen swimming up falls and rivers. It metes out staggering damage with its single horn.

name: Seaking
pokedex_description: It punches holes in boulders on stream- beds. This is a clever innovation that prevents its eggs from being attacked or washed away by the current.

name: Staryu
pokedex_description: It gathers with others in the night and makes its red core glow on and off with the twinkling stars. It can regenerate limbs if they are severed from its body.

name: Starmie
pokedex_description: People in ancient times imagined that Starmie were transformed from the reflections of stars that twinkled on gentle waves at night.

name: Mr. Mime
pokedex_description: A Mr. Mime is a master of pantomime. It can convince others that something unseeable actually exists. Once believed, the imaginary object does become real.

name: Scyther
pokedex_description: Its blindingly fast speed adds to the sharpness of its twin forearm scythes. The scythes can slice through thick logs in one wicked stroke.

name: Jynx
pokedex_description: Fueron traídas de las Américas para servir en algunos espectáculos de la corte. Con el tiempo se fueron adaptando al arte del sur de Iberia.

name: Electabuzz
pokedex_description: When a storm approaches, it competes with others to scale heights that are likely to be stricken by lightning. Some towns use Electabuzz in place of lightning rods.

name: Magmar
pokedex_description: In battle, it blows out intense flames from all over its body to intimidate its foe. These fiery bursts create heat waves that ignite grass and trees in the area.

name: Pinsir
pokedex_description: Their pincers are strong enough to shatter thick logs. Because they dislike cold, Pinsir burrow and sleep under the ground on chilly nights.

name: Tauros
pokedex_description: It is not satisfied unless it is rampaging at all times. If there is no opponent for Tauros to battle, it will charge at thick trees and knock them down to calm itself.

name: Magikarp
pokedex_description: Its swimming muscles are weak, so it is easily washed away by currents. In places where water pools, you can see many Magikarp deposited there by the flow.

name: Gyarados
pokedex_description: It is an extremely vicious and violent Pokémon. When humans begin to fight, it will appear and burn everything to the ground with intensely hot flames.

name: Lapras
pokedex_description: People have driven Lapras almost to the point of extinction. In the evenings, it is said to sing plaintively as it seeks what few others of its kind still remain.

name: Ditto
pokedex_description: A Ditto rearranges its cell structure to transform itself. However, if it tries to change based on its memory, it will get details wrong.

name: Eevee
pokedex_description: Tiene mecanismos celulares que inducen la producción de mutaciones en el genoma cuando es expuesto a diferentes estímulos, como forma de adaptación.

name: Vaporeon
pokedex_description: Muy ágil en tierra firme y en el agua gracias a su aleta caudal. Además de pulmones posee branquias alrededor del cuello para respirar bajo agua.

name: Jolteon
pokedex_description: Se mueve a una velocidad vertiginosa, gracias a lo cual se carga de electricidad estática por el rozamiento con el aire, erizándose así su pelaje.

name: Flareon
pokedex_description: Es pacífico, calmado y muy suave. El calor que produce depende de su estado de ánimo, produciendo más si está enfadado o asustado.

name: Porygon
pokedex_description: It is capable of reverting itself entirely back to program data in order to enter cyberspace. A Porygon is copy- protected so it cannot be duplicated.

name: Omanyte
pokedex_description: One of the ancient and long-since-extinct Pokémon that have been regenerated from fossils by humans. If attacked, it withdraws into its hard shell.

name: Omastar
pokedex_description: An Omastar uses its tentacles to capture its prey. It is believed to have become extinct because its shell grew too large, making its movements slow and ponderous.

name: Kabuto
pokedex_description: It is a Pokémon that has been regenerated from a fossil. However, in rare cases, living examples have been discovered. Kabuto have not changed for 300 million years.

name: Kabutops
pokedex_description: Kabutops once swam underwater to hunt for prey. It was apparently evolving from being a water dweller to living on land as evident from changes in its gills and legs.

name: Aerodactyl
pokedex_description: Aerodactyl is a Pokémon from the age of dinosaurs. It was regenerated from DNA extracted from amber. It is imagined to have been the king of the skies.

name: Snorlax
pokedex_description: Snorlax's typical day consists of nothing more than eating and sleeping. It is such a docile Pokémon that there are children who use its big belly as a place to play.

name: Articuno
pokedex_description: Articuno is a legendary bird Pokémon that can control ice. The flapping of its wings chills the air. As a result, it is said that when this Pokémon flies, snow will fall.

name: Zapdos
pokedex_description: Zapdos is a legendary bird Pokémon that has the ability to control electricity. It usually lives in thunderclouds. It gains power if it is stricken by lightning bolts.

name: Moltres
pokedex_description: Moltres is a legendary bird Pokémon that can control fire. If injured, it is said to dip its body in the molten magma of a volcano to burn and heal itself.

name: Dratini
pokedex_description: A Dratini continually molts and sloughs off its old skin. It does so because the life energy within its body steadily builds to reach uncontrollable levels.

name: Dragonair
pokedex_description: A Dragonair stores an enormous amount of energy inside its body. It is said to alter the weather around it by loosing energy from the crystals on its neck and tail.

name: Dragonite
pokedex_description: It can circle the globe in just 16 hours. It is a kindhearted Pokémon that leads lost and foundering ships in a storm to the safety of land.

name: Mewtwo
pokedex_description: A Pokémon that was created by genetic manipulation. However, even though the scientific power of humans made its body, they failed to give it a warm heart.

name: Mew
pokedex_description: A Mew is said to possess the genes of all Pokémon. It is capable of making itself invisible at will, so it entirely avoids notice even if it approaches people.

name: Chikorita
pokedex_description: It waves its leaf around to keep foes at bay. However, a sweet fragrance also wafts from the leaf, creating a friendly atmosphere that becalms the battlers.

name: Bayleef
pokedex_description: A Bayleef's neck is ringed by curled-up leaves. Inside each leaf is a small tree shoot. The fragrance of this shoot makes people peppy.

name: Meganium
pokedex_description: The fragrance of a Meganium's flower soothes and calms emotions. In battle, it gives off more of its becalming scent to blunt the foe's fighting spirit.

name: Cyndaquil
pokedex_description: It flares flames from its back to protect itself. The fire burns vigorously if the Pokémon is angry. When it is tired, it sputters with incomplete combustion.

name: Quilava
pokedex_description: It intimidates foes with intense gusts of flames and superheated air. Its quick nimbleness lets it dodge attacks even while scorching an enemy.

name: Typhlosion
pokedex_description: It can hide behind a shimmering heat haze that it creates using its intense flames. Typhlosion create blazing explosive blasts that burn everything to cinders.

name: Totodile
pokedex_description: Despite its small body, Totodile's jaws are very powerful. While it may think it is just playfully nipping, its bite has enough strength to cause serious injury.

name: Croconaw
pokedex_description: Once its jaws clamp down on its foe, it will absolutely not let go. Because the tips of its fangs are forked back like fishhooks, they become irremovably embedded.

name: Feraligatr
pokedex_description: It opens its huge mouth to intimidate enemies. In battle, it runs using its thick and powerful hind legs to charge the foe with incredible speed.

name: Sentret
pokedex_description: They take turns standing guard when it is time to sleep. The sentry awakens the others if it senses danger. If one becomes separated, it turns sleepless with fear.

name: Furret
pokedex_description: A Furret has a very slim build. When under attack, it can squirm through narrow spaces and get away. In spite of its short limbs, it is very nimble and fleet.

name: Hoothoot
pokedex_description: It has an internal organ that senses the earth's rotation. Using this special organ, a Hoothoot begins hooting at precisely the same time every day.

name: Noctowl
pokedex_description: It unfailingly catches prey in darkness. Noctowl owe their success to superior vision that allows them to see in minimal light, and to their supple and silent wings.

name: Ledyba
pokedex_description: Ledyba communicate using a fluid that they secrete from where the legs join the body. They are said to convey feelings to others by altering the fluid's scent.

name: Ledian
pokedex_description: It is said that in lands with clean air, where the stars fill the sky, there live many Ledian. For good reason, they use the light of the stars as energy.

name: Spinarak
pokedex_description: The web it spins can be considered its second nervous system. It is said that a Spinarak determines its prey by the tiny vibrations it feels through the web.

name: Ariados
pokedex_description: Its feet are tipped with tiny hooked claws that enable it to scuttle on ceilings and vertical walls. It constricts its foe with thin and strong silk webbing.

name: Crobat
pokedex_description: Over the course of evolution, its hind legs turned into wings. By alternately resting its front and rear wings, it can fly all day without having to stop.

name: Chinchou
pokedex_description: When it senses danger, it discharges positive and negative electricity from its two antennae. It lives in depths beyond sunlight's reach.

name: Lanturn
pokedex_description: The light-emitting orbs on its back are very bright. They are formed from a part of its dorsal fin. This Pokémon illuminates the inky darkness of deep seas.

name: Pichu
pokedex_description: It is still inept at retaining electricity. When it is startled, it discharges power accidentally. It gets better at holding power as it grows older.

name: Cleffa
pokedex_description: On nights with many shooting stars, Cleffa can be seen dancing in a ring. They dance until daybreak, when they quench their thirst with the morning dew.

name: Igglybuff
pokedex_description: Le gusta mucho cantar y cuida muy bien la salud de su garganta. Si tropieza empezará a rebotar como un balón de playa y le costará parar.

name: Togepi
pokedex_description: As its energy, it uses the feelings of compassion and pleasure exuded by people and Pokémon. It stores up happy feelings in its shell, then shares them out.

name: Togetic
pokedex_description: It is said to be a Pokémon that brings good fortune. When it spots someone who is pure of heart, a Togetic appears and shares its happiness with that person.

name: Natu
pokedex_description: It runs up short trees that grow on the savanna to peck at new shoots. A Natu's eyes look as if they are always observing something.

name: Xatu
pokedex_description: It has the enigmatic power of foreseeing the future. Some people in different lands have long believed that Xatu are emissaries from another world.

name: Mareep
pokedex_description: Its fluffy wool rubs together and builds a static charge. The more energy is charged, the more brightly the lightbulb at the tip of its tail glows.

name: Flaaffy
pokedex_description: Its fleece quality changes to generate strong static electricity with a small amount of wool. The bare, slick parts of its hide are shielded against electricity.

name: Ampharos
pokedex_description: It gives off so much light that it can be seen even from space. People in the old days used its light to send signals back and forth with others far away.

name: Bellossom
pokedex_description: Its flower petals deepen in color through exposure to sunlight. When cloudy weather persists, it does a dance that is thought to be a ritual for summoning the sun.

name: Marill
pokedex_description: Its body is covered with water-repellent fur. Because of the fur, it can swim through water at high speed without being slowed by the water's resistance.

name: Azumarill
pokedex_description: It lives in water virtually all day long. Its body color and pattern act as camouflage that makes it tough for enemies to spot in water.

name: Sudowoodo
pokedex_description: It mimics a tree to avoid being attacked by enemies. But since its forelegs remain green throughout the year, it is easily identified as a fake in the winter.

name: Politoed
pokedex_description: The curled hair on its head proves its status as a king. It is said that the longer and curlier the hair, the more respect it earns from its peers.

name: Hoppip
pokedex_description: This Pokémon drifts and floats with the wind. If it senses the approach of strong winds, a Hoppip links leaves with others to prepare against being blown away.

name: Skiploom
pokedex_description: It blossoms when the temperature rises above 64 degrees F. Because its flower's blooming changes with the temperature, it is sometimes used as a thermometer.

name: Jumpluff
pokedex_description: Jumpluff ride warm southern winds to cross the sea and fly to foreign lands. This Pokémon lands when it encounters cold air while it is floating.

name: Aipom
pokedex_description: Its tail ends with a dexterous, handlike appendage. However, because it uses the tail so much, Aipom's real hands have become rather clumsy.

name: Sunkern
pokedex_description: Sunkern try to minimize movement to conserve the nutrients they have stored in their bodies for evolution. They will not eat, subsisting only on morning dew.

name: Sunflora
pokedex_description: Sunflora convert solar energy into nutrition. They are highly active in the warm daytime but suddenly stop moving as soon as the sun sets.

name: Yanma
pokedex_description: It can see 360 degrees without moving its eyes. It is a great flier capable of making sudden stops and turning midair to quickly chase down targeted prey.

name: Wooper
pokedex_description: Wooper usually live in water but come out onto land seeking food occasionally. On land, they coat their bodies with a gooey, toxic film.

name: Quagsire
pokedex_description: A Quagsire hunts by leaving its mouth wide open in water and waiting for its prey to blunder in. Because it doesn't move, it does not get very hungry.

name: Espeon
pokedex_description: Su cola bífida le sirve para apoyarse y caminar a 2 patas o llegar más alto. Desarrolla grandes poderes psíquicos que potencia con la gema de su frente.

name: Umbreon
pokedex_description: Está completamente adaptado a la vida nocturna, pudiendo ver incluso mejor de noche que de día. Puede ocultarse perfectamente en la oscuridad.

name: Murkrow
pokedex_description: Murkrow were feared as the alleged bearers of ill fortune. It shows strong interest in anything that sparkles. It will even try to steal rings from women.

name: Slowking
pokedex_description: It undertakes research every day to solve the mysteries of the world. However, it apparently forgets everything if the Shellder on its head comes off.

name: Misdreavus
pokedex_description: A Misdreavus frightens people with a creepy, sobbing cry. It apparently uses its red spheres to absorb the fear of foes as its nutrition.

name: Unown
pokedex_description: This Pokémon is shaped like ancient text characters. Although research is ongoing, it is a mystery as to which came first, the ancient writings or the various Unown.

name: Wobbuffet
pokedex_description: Usually docile, a Wobbuffet strikes back ferociously if its black tail is attacked. It makes its lair in caves where it waits for nightfall.

name: Girafarig
pokedex_description: A Girafarig is an herbivore--it eats grass and tree shoots. While it is eating, its tail makes chewing and swallowing motions as if it were also eating.

name: Pineco
pokedex_description: A Pineco hangs from a tree branch and waits for prey. While eating, if it is disturbed by someone shaking its tree, it falls on the ground and suddenly explodes.

name: Forretress
pokedex_description: It keeps itself inside its steel shell. The shell is opened when it is catching prey, but it is so quick that the shell's inside cannot be seen.

name: Dunsparce
pokedex_description: Its drill-tipped tail is used to burrow into the ground backwards. This Pokémon is known to make its nest in complex shapes deep under the ground.

name: Gligar
pokedex_description: It glides without making a single sound. It grasps the face of its foe using its hind and large front claws, then stabs with its poison barb.

name: Steelix
pokedex_description: Steelix live even further underground than Onix. This Pokémon is known to dig toward the earth's core, reaching a depth of over six-tenths of a mile underground.

name: Snubbull
pokedex_description: By baring its fangs and making a scary face, it sends smaller Pokémon scurrying in terror. The Snubbull does seem a little sad at making its foes flee.

name: Granbull
pokedex_description: It has a particularly well-developed lower jaw. The huge fangs are heavy, causing it to tilt its head. Unless it is startled, it will not try to bite.

name: Qwilfish
pokedex_description: A Qwilfish uses the pressure of water it swallows to shoot toxic quills all at once from all over its body. It finds swimming to be somewhat challenging.

name: Scizor
pokedex_description: A Scizor has a body with the hardness of steel. It is not easily fazed by ordinary sorts of attacks. It flaps its wings to regulate its body temperature.

name: Shuckle
pokedex_description: A Shuckle hides under rocks, keeping its body concealed inside its shell while eating stored berries. The berries mix with its body fluids to become a juice.

name: Heracross
pokedex_description: They gather in forests seeking the sweet sap of trees. It is completely clad in a steel-hard shell. It is proud of its horn, which it uses to fling foes.

name: Sneasel
pokedex_description: A Sneasel scales trees by punching its hooked claws into the bark. It seeks out unguarded nests and steals eggs for food while the parents are away.

name: Teddiursa
pokedex_description: It licks its palms that are sweetened by being soaked in honey. A Teddiursa makes its own honey by blending fruits and pollen collected by Beedrill.

name: Ursaring
pokedex_description: In forests, it is said that there are many streams and towering trees where an Ursaring gathers food. It walks through its forest collecting food every day.

name: Slugma
pokedex_description: It is a species of Pokémon that lives in volcanic areas. If its body cools, its skin hardens and immobilizes it. To avoid that, it sleeps near magma.

name: Magcargo
pokedex_description: The shell on its back is made of hardened magma. Tens of thousands of years spent living in volcanic craters have turned Magcargo's bodies into magma.

name: Swinub
pokedex_description: It roots for food by rubbing its snout against the ground. Its favorite food is a mushroom that grows under dried grass. It occasionally roots out hot springs.

name: Piloswine
pokedex_description: A Piloswine is covered by a thick coat of long hair for enduring freezing cold. It uses its tusks to dig up food that has been buried under ice.

name: Corsola
pokedex_description: Corsola live in warm southern seas. If the sea becomes polluted, the beautiful coral stalks become discolored and crumble away in tatters.

name: Remoraid
pokedex_description: A Remoraid uses its abdominal muscles to forcefully expel swallowed water, then shoot down flying prey. When evolution approaches, it travels down rivers.

name: Octillery
pokedex_description: It ensnares its foe with its suction- cupped tentacles before delivering the finishing blow. If the foe turns out to be too strong, it spews ink to escape.

name: Delibird
pokedex_description: It carries food bundled up in its tail. There was a famous explorer who managed to scale Mt. Everest thanks to a Delibird sharing its food.

name: Mantine
pokedex_description: On sunny days, schools of Mantine can be seen elegantly leaping over the waves. It is not bothered by the Remoraid that hitches rides.

name: Skarmory
pokedex_description: A Pokémon that has a body and wings of steel. People in the past used feathers fallen from Skarmory to make swords and knives.

name: Houndour
pokedex_description: Houndour communicate with each other using a variety of cries to corner their prey. This Pokémon's remarkable teamwork is simply unparalleled.

name: Houndoom
pokedex_description: In a Houndoom pack, the one with its horns raked sharply back serves a leadership role. They choose their leader by fighting among themselves.

name: Kingdra
pokedex_description: It sleeps quietly, deep on the seafloor. When it comes up to the surface, it creates a huge whirlpool that can swallow even ships.

name: Phanpy
pokedex_description: Phanpy's big ears serve as broad fans. When it becomes hot, it flaps the ears busily to cool down. Even the young are very strong.

name: Donphan
pokedex_description: A Donphan is so strong it can easily haul a dump truck. Its hide has toughened to a rock-hard state. An ordinary sort of attack won't even leave a scratch.

name: Porygon2
pokedex_description: It was created by humans using the power of science. It has been given artificial intelligence that enables it to learn new gestures and emotions on its own.

name: Stantler
pokedex_description: Stantler's magnificent antlers were once traded at high prices as works of art. As a result, this Pokémon was hunted close to extinction.

name: Smeargle
pokedex_description: Es un artista nato, todos los grandes pintores de la historia de Iberia han tenido uno como compañero que les ayudaba a crear sus obras de arte.

name: Tyrogue
pokedex_description: Tyrogue become stressed out if they do not get to train every day. When raising this Pokémon, the trainer must establish a regular training schedule.

name: Hitmontop
pokedex_description: Its technique of kicking while spinning is a remarkable mix of both offense and defense. Hitmontop travel faster spinning than they do walking.

name: Smoochum
pokedex_description: Es muy presumida y desde pequeña aprende el arte del coqueteo para llamar la atención y conseguir lo que quiere mostrándose adorable.

name: Elekid
pokedex_description: If it touches metal and discharges the electricity it has stored in its body, an Elekid begins swinging its arms in circles to recharge itself.

name: Magby
pokedex_description: If a Magby is spouting yellow flames from its mouth, it is in good health. When it is fatigued, black smoke will be mixed in with the flames.

name: Miltank
pokedex_description: It gives over five gallons of milk daily. Its sweet milk is enjoyed by children and grown-ups alike. People who can't drink milk turn it into yogurt and eat it instead.

name: Blissey
pokedex_description: If it senses sadness with its fluffy fur, a Blissey will rush over to the sad person, however far away, to share an egg of happiness that brings a smile to any face.

name: Raikou
pokedex_description: Raikou embodies the speed of lightning. Its roars send shock waves shuddering through the air and ground as if lightning bolts were crashing down.

name: Entei
pokedex_description: Entei embodies the passion of magma. It is thought to have been born in the eruption of a volcano. It blasts fire that consumes all that it touches.

name: Suicune
pokedex_description: Suicune embodies the compassion of a pure spring of water. It runs across the land with gliding elegance. It has the power to purify dirty water.

name: Larvitar
pokedex_description: A Larvitar is born deep under the ground. It must eat its way through the soil above and reach the surface for it to see its parents' faces.

name: Pupitar
pokedex_description: A Pupitar creates a gas inside its body that it ejects under compression to propel itself like a jet. Its body can withstand a collision with solid steel.

name: Tyranitar
pokedex_description: A Tyranitar is so overwhelmingly powerful, it can bring down a whole mountain to make its nest. It roams in mountains seeking new opponents to fight.

name: Lugia
pokedex_description: Lugia is so powerful even a light fluttering of its wings can blow apart houses. As a result, it chooses to live out of sight deep under the sea.

name: Ho-Oh
pokedex_description: Its feathers--which glow in seven colors depending on the angle at which they are struck by light--are thought to bring joy. It is said to live at the foot of a rainbow.

name: Celebi
pokedex_description: This Pokémon came from the future by crossing over time. It is thought that so long as Celebi appears, a bright and shining future awaits us.

name: Treecko
pokedex_description: It makes its nest in a giant tree in the forest. It ferociously guards against anything nearing its territory. It is said to be the protector of the forest's trees.

name: Grovyle
pokedex_description: Leaves grow out of this Pokémon's body. They help obscure a Grovyle from the eyes of its enemies while it is in a thickly overgrown forest.

name: Sceptile
pokedex_description: In the jungle, its power is without equal. This Pokémon carefully grows trees and plants. It regulates its body temperature by basking in sunlight.

name: Torchic
pokedex_description: If attacked, it strikes back by spitting balls of fire it forms in its stomach. A Torchic dislikes darkness because it can't see its surroundings.

name: Combusken
pokedex_description: It lashes out with 10 kicks per second. Its strong fighting instinct compels it to keep up its offensive until the opponent gives up.

name: Blaziken
pokedex_description: It learns martial arts that use punches and kicks. Every several years, its old feathers burn off, and new, supple feathers grow back in their place.

name: Mudkip
pokedex_description: On land, it can powerfully lift large boulders by planting its four feet and heaving. It sleeps by burying itself in soil at the water's edge.

name: Marshtomp
pokedex_description: Its toughened hind legs enable it to stand upright. Because it weakens if its skin dries out, it replenishes fluids by playing in mud.

name: Swampert
pokedex_description: If it senses the approach of a storm and a tidal wave, it protects its seaside nest by piling up boulders. It swims as fast as a jet ski.

name: Poochyena
pokedex_description: It savagely threatens foes with bared fangs. It chases after fleeing targets tenaciously. It turns tail and runs, however, if the foe strikes back.

name: Mightyena
pokedex_description: In the wild, Mightyena live in a pack. They never defy their leader's orders. They defeat foes with perfectly coordinated teamwork.

name: Zigzagoon
pokedex_description: Rubbing its nose against the ground, it always wanders about back and forth in search of something. It is distinguished by the zigzag footprints it leaves.

name: Linoone
pokedex_description: It is exceedingly fast if it only has to run in a straight line. When it spots pond- dwelling prey underwater, it quickly leaps in and catches it with its sharp claws.

name: Wurmple
pokedex_description: It sticks to tree branches and eats leaves. The thread it spits from its mouth, which becomes gooey when it touches air, slows the movement of its foes.

name: Silcoon
pokedex_description: It prepares for evolution using the energy it stored while it was a Wurmple. It keeps watch over the surroundings with its two eyes.

name: Beautifly
pokedex_description: Its colorfully patterned wings are its most prominent feature. It flies through flower-covered fields collecting pollen. It attacks ferociously when angered.

name: Cascoon
pokedex_description: To avoid detection by its enemies, it hides motionlessly beneath large leaves and in the gaps of branches. It also attaches dead leaves to its body for camouflage.

name: Dustox
pokedex_description: It is a nocturnal Pokémon that flies from fields and mountains to the attraction of streetlights at night. It looses highly toxic powder from its wings.

name: Lotad
pokedex_description: This Pokémon lives in ponds with clean water. It is known to ferry small Pokémon across ponds by carrying them on the broad leaf on its head.

name: Lombre
pokedex_description: In the evening, it takes great delight in popping out of rivers and startling people. It feeds on aquatic moss that grows on rocks in the riverbed.

name: Ludicolo
pokedex_description: When it hears festive music, all the cells in its body become stimulated, and it begins moving in rhythm. It does not quail even when it faces a tough opponent.

name: Seedot
pokedex_description: Es presa de varios Pokémon por lo que suelen colgarse de árboles y ocultarse entre las hojas para absorber la savia elaborada sin peligro.

name: Nuzleaf
pokedex_description: Usa la hoja de su cabeza para soplar y realizar sonidos diversos que le sirven para comunicarse entre ellos, confundir a sus enemigos, etc.

name: Shiftry
pokedex_description: Lidera grupos de Nuzleaf y se preocupa por sus compañeros. Puede usar los abanicos de sus brazos para planear o provocar fuertes vientos.

name: Taillow
pokedex_description: Although it is small, it is very courageous. It will take on a larger Skarmory on an equal footing. However, its will weakens if it becomes hungry.

name: Swellow
pokedex_description: A Swellow dives upon prey from far above. It never misses its targets. It takes to the skies in search of lands with a warm climate.

name: Wingull
pokedex_description: It makes its nest on a sheer cliff at the edge of the sea. It has trouble keeping its wings flapping in flight. Instead, it soars on updrafts.

name: Pelipper
pokedex_description: It skims the tops of waves as it flies. When it spots prey, it uses its large beak to scoop up the victim with water. It protects its eggs in its beak.

name: Ralts
pokedex_description: A Ralts has the power to sense the emotions of people and Pokémon with the horns on its head. It takes cover if it senses any hostility.

name: Kirlia
pokedex_description: A Kirlia has the psychic power to create a rip in the dimensions and see into the future. It is said to dance with pleasure on sunny mornings.

name: Gardevoir
pokedex_description: It apparently does not feel the pull of gravity because it supports itself with psychic power. It will give its life to protect its trainer.

name: Surskit
pokedex_description: They gather on puddles after evening downpours, gliding across the surface of water as if sliding. It secretes honey with a sweet aroma from its head.

name: Masquerain
pokedex_description: It intimidates foes with the large eyelike patterns on its antennae. Because it can't fly if its wings get wet, it shelters itself from rain under large trees and eaves.

name: Shroomish
pokedex_description: It loves to eat damp, composted soil in forests. If you enter a forest after a long rain, you can see many Shroomish feasting on composted soil.

name: Breloom
pokedex_description: It scatters spores from holes in the cap on its head. It loves warm and humid climates. It feeds on trees and plants in fields and forests.

name: Slakoth
pokedex_description: It sleeps virtually all day and night long. It doesn't change its nest its entire life, but it sometimes travels great distances by swimming in rivers.

name: Vigoroth
pokedex_description: It can't keep still because its blood boils with energy. It runs through the fields and mountains all day to calm itself. If it doesn't, it can't sleep at night.

name: Slaking
pokedex_description: Hordes of Slaking gather around trees when fruits come into season. They wait around patiently for ripened fruits to fall out of the trees.

name: Nincada
pokedex_description: It makes its nest at the roots of a mighty tree. Using its whiskerlike antennae, it probes its surroundings in the pitch-black darkness of soil.

name: Ninjask
pokedex_description: Because it darts about vigorously at high speed, it is very difficult to see. Hearing its distinctive cries for too long induces a headache.

name: Shedinja
pokedex_description: A peculiar Pokémon that floats in air even though its wings remain completely still. The inside of its body is hollow and utterly dark.

name: Whismur
pokedex_description: Its cries equal a jet plane in volume. It inhales through its ear canals. Because of this system, it can cry continually without having to catch its breath.

name: Loudred
pokedex_description: It positions the round speakers on its head to assail foes with ultrasonic waves at massive volume. It builds power by stomping the ground.

name: Exploud
pokedex_description: It has sound-generating organs all over its body. It communicates with others by adjusting the tone and volume of the cries it emits.

name: Makuhita
pokedex_description: It loves to toughen up its body above all else. If you hear quaking rumbles in a cave, it is the sound of Makuhita undertaking strenuous training.

name: Hariyama
pokedex_description: It has the habit of challenging others without hesitation to tests of strength. It's been known to stand on train tracks and stop trains using forearm thrusts.

name: Azurill
pokedex_description: Its tail, which is packed with nutrition, is very bouncy like a rubber ball. On sunny days they gather at the edge of water and splash about for fun.

name: Nosepass
pokedex_description: Its body emits a powerful magnetism. It feeds on prey that is pulled in by the force. Its magnetism is stronger in cold seasons.

name: Skitty
pokedex_description: A Skitty's adorably cute behavior makes it highly popular. In battle, it makes its tail puff out. It threatens foes with a sharp growl.

name: Delcatty
pokedex_description: Rather than keeping a permanent lair, it habitually seeks comfortable spots and sleeps there. It is nocturnal and becomes active at dusk.

name: Sableye
pokedex_description: It digs branching holes in caves using its sharp claws in search of food--raw gems. A Sableye lurks in darkness and is seen only rarely.

name: Mawile
pokedex_description: Its giant jaws are actually steel horns that transformed. It fools foes into complacency with its adorable gestures, then chomps them with its huge jaws.

name: Aron
pokedex_description: A Pokémon that is clad in steel armor. A new suit of armor is made when it evolves. The old, discarded armor is salvaged as metal for making iron products.

name: Lairon
pokedex_description: When two Lairon meet in the wild, they fight for territory by bashing into each other with their steel bodies. The sound of their collision carries for miles.

name: Aggron
pokedex_description: Its iron horns grow longer a little at a time. They are used to determine the Aggron's age. The gouges in its armor are worn with pride as mementos from battles.

name: Meditite
pokedex_description: It continually meditates for hours every day. As a result of rigorous and dedicated yoga training, it has tempered its spiritual power so much it can fly.

name: Medicham
pokedex_description: Through crushingly harsh yoga training, it gained the power to foretell its foe's actions. It battles with elegant, dance- like movement.

name: Electrike
pokedex_description: It generates electricity using friction from the atmosphere. In seasons with especially arid air, its entire body blazes with violent showers of sparks.

name: Manectric
pokedex_description: Because lightning falls in their vicinities, Manectric were thought to have been born from lightning. In battle, they create thunderclouds.

name: Plusle
pokedex_description: It has the trait of cheering on its fellow Pokémon. By shorting out the electricity it releases from its paws, it creates pom-poms for cheering.

name: Minun
pokedex_description: At a meeting of Pokémon academics, it was announced that simultaneous exposure to electricity from a Plusle and Minun will promote circulation and boost vitality.

name: Volbeat
pokedex_description: With their taillights lit, Volbeat fly in a swarm, drawing geometric designs in the night sky. They move their nests if their pond water becomes dirty.

name: Illumise
pokedex_description: A nocturnal Pokémon that becomes active upon nightfall. It leads a Volbeat swarm to draw patterns in the night sky. Over 200 different patterns have been confirmed.

name: Roselia
pokedex_description: A Roselia that drinks nutritionally rich springwater blooms with lovely flowers. The fragrance of its flowers has the effect of making its foes careless.

name: Gulpin
pokedex_description: This Pokémon's stomach fluid can even digest scrap iron. In one gulp, it can swallow something that is as large as itself.

name: Swalot
pokedex_description: Its powerful stomach acid is capable of digesting almost anything. The one thing in the whole world a Swalot can't digest is its own stomach.

name: Carvanha
pokedex_description: Carvanha attack ships in swarms, making them sink. Although it is said to be a very vicious Pokémon, it timidly flees as soon as it finds itself alone.

name: Sharpedo
pokedex_description: The vicious and sly gangster of the sea. Its skin is specially textured to minimize drag in water. Its speed tops out at over 75 miles per hour.

name: Wailmer
pokedex_description: While this Pokémon usually lives in the sea, it can survive on land, although not too long. It loses vitality if its body becomes dried out.

name: Wailord
pokedex_description: It breathes through nostrils that it raises above the sea. By inhaling to its maximum capacity, a Wailord can dive close to 10,000 feet beneath the waves.

name: Numel
pokedex_description: En las plantas de las patas tiene callosidades para resistir el calor del suelo. En la joroba guardan grasa que estalla para atacar al calentarse.

name: Camerupt
pokedex_description: Es pacífico pero se irrita rápido, si se le molesta escupe magma. Puede guardar grasa en sus jorobas y alimentarse de ella durante 10 días.

name: Torkoal
pokedex_description: It battles using energy it gets from burning coal. When loosing smoke from its nostrils, it lets off a sound that is similar to a locomotive's horn.

name: Spoink
pokedex_description: A Pokémon that manipulates psychic power at will. It doesn't stop bouncing even when it is asleep. It loves eating mushrooms that grow underground.

name: Grumpig
pokedex_description: It stores power in the black pearls on its forehead. When it uses psychic power, it performs an odd dance step. Its style of dancing became hugely popular overseas.

name: Spinda
pokedex_description: It is distinguished by a pattern of spots that is always different. Its unsteady, tottering walk has the effect of fouling its foe's aim.

name: Trapinch
pokedex_description: Excava un hoyo en forma de embudo en cuyo fondo se esconde, sus presas al caer en él no pueden salir y terminan dentro de sus grandes mandíbulas.

name: Vibrava
pokedex_description: A pesar de disminuir el tamaño de su mandíbula, tiene mucha fuerza en ella. Son depredadores que cazan incluso Pokémon de su propia especie.

name: Flygon
pokedex_description: Se comunican a grandes distancias por medio de feromonas. Suelen esconder sus huevos ligeramente enterrados o entre la vegetación.

name: Cacnea
pokedex_description: Cacnea live in deserts with virtually no rainfall. It battles by swinging its thick, spiked arms. Once a year, a yellow flower blooms.

name: Cacturne
pokedex_description: After spending thousands of years in harsh deserts, its blood transformed into the same substances as sand. It is nocturnal, so it hunts at night.

name: Swablu
pokedex_description: Es uno de los Pokémon con migraciones más largas y mayores bandadas. Su cuerpo le permite viajar grandes distancias pasando inadvertido.

name: Altaria
pokedex_description: Le gustan los territorios cálidos y en los que pueda encontrar mucha fruta. Migra buscando esos territorios siendo el líder de las bandadas de Swablu.

name: Zangoose
pokedex_description: When it battles, it stands on its hind legs and attacks with its sharply clawed forelegs. Its fur bristles if it encounters any Seviper.

name: Seviper
pokedex_description: Seviper and Zangoose are eternal rivals. It counters a Zangoose's dazzling agility with its swordlike tail, which also oozes a horrible poison.

name: Lunatone
pokedex_description: It becomes very active on the night of a full moon. This Pokémon was first discovered 40 years ago at the site of a meteor strike.

name: Solrock
pokedex_description: Solar energy is the source of this Pokémon's power. On sunny days, groups of Solrock line up facing the sun and absorb its light.

name: Barboach
pokedex_description: Its body is covered with a slimy film. The film acts as a barrier to prevent germs in muddy water from entering the Barboach's body.

name: Whiscash
pokedex_description: Mysteriously, it can foretell earthquakes. In the daytime, it sleeps in mud at the bottom of a pond. When it awakens, it continually feeds throughout the night.

name: Corphish
pokedex_description: Once it grips prey with its large pincers, it will never let go, no matter what. It is a hardy Pokémon that can thrive in any environment.

name: Crawdaunt
pokedex_description: A brutish Pokémon that loves to battle. A veteran Crawdaunt that has prevailed in hundreds of battles has giant pincers marked with countless scars.

name: Baltoy
pokedex_description: A Baltoy moves by spinning on its single foot. It has been depicted in murals adorning the walls of a once-bustling city in an ancient age.

name: Claydol
pokedex_description: A Claydol sleeps while hovering in midair. Its arms are separate from its body. They are kept floating by the Pokémon's manipulation of psychic power.

name: Lileep
pokedex_description: It disguises itself as seaweed by making its tentacles sway. Unsuspecting prey that come too close are swallowed whole. It became extinct 100 million years ago.

name: Cradily
pokedex_description: It drags its heavy body along the seafloor. It makes its nest in the shallows of warm seas. Cradily can be seen on beaches when the tide goes out.

name: Anorith
pokedex_description: It was resurrected from a fossil using the power of science. It swims by undulating the eight wings at its sides. They were feet that adapted to life in the sea.

name: Armaldo
pokedex_description: Armaldo usually lives on land. However, when it hunts for prey, it dives beneath the ocean. It swims around using its two large wings.

name: Feebas
pokedex_description: Feebas live in ponds that are heavily infested with weeds. Because of its hopelessly shabby appearance, it seems as if few trainers raise it.

name: Milotic
pokedex_description: It is said to live at the bottom of large lakes. Considered to be the most beautiful of all Pokémon, it has been depicted in paintings and statues.

name: Castform
pokedex_description: It alters its form depending on the weather. Changes in the climate such as the temperature and humidity appear to affect its cellular structure.

name: Kecleon
pokedex_description: A Pokémon that has the ability to alter its body colors to match its surroundings. A Kecleon reverts to its original colors if it is startled.

name: Shuppet
pokedex_description: This Pokémon roams about deep in the night seeking such negative emotions as grudges and envy. It retreats to its nest when the sun begins to rise.

name: Banette
pokedex_description: An abandoned plush doll became this Pokémon. They are said to live in garbage dumps and wander about in search of the children that threw them away.

name: Duskull
pokedex_description: A glare from its single scarlet eye makes even burly grown-ups freeze in utter fear. It is a nocturnal Pokémon that roams about under the cloak of darkness.

name: Dusclops
pokedex_description: It is thought that its body is hollow with only a spectral ball of fire burning inside. However, no one has been able to confirm this theory as fact.

name: Tropius
pokedex_description: It flies by flapping its broad leaves. The bunch of fruit that grows around its neck is deliciously sweet. In the spring, it scatters pollen from its neck.

name: Chimecho
pokedex_description: They fly about very actively when the hot season arrives. They communicate among themselves using seven different and distinguishing cries.

name: Absol
pokedex_description: It sharply senses even subtle changes in the sky and the land to predict natural disasters. It is a long-lived Pokémon that has a life-span of 100 years.

name: Wynaut
pokedex_description: A Wynaut loves to eat sweet fruits. It cleverly picks fruits using its earlike arms. They gather in fruit gardens, drawn by the fragrance.

name: Snorunt
pokedex_description: Fueron introducidos en Iberia por los japoneses de Coria del Rio en 1614. Habita en zonas nevadas y usa un traje japonés tradicional de invierno.

name: Glalie
pokedex_description: Es un gran depredador adaptado a montañas nevadas y cuevas heladas, congela a sus presas antes de comérselas con su fuerte mandíbula.

name: Spheal
pokedex_description: It is completely covered with plushy fur. As a result, it never feels the cold even when it is rolling about on ice floes or diving in the sea.

name: Sealeo
pokedex_description: Sealeo live in herds on ice floes. Using its powerful flippers, it shatters ice. It dives into the sea to hunt prey five times a day.

name: Walrein
pokedex_description: To protect its herd, the leader battles anything that invades its territory, even at the cost of its life. Its tusks may snap off in battle.

name: Clamperl
pokedex_description: A Clamperl slams its shell closed on prey to prevent escape. The pearl it creates upon evolution is said to be infused with a mysterious energy.

name: Huntail
pokedex_description: To withstand the crushing pressure of water deep under the sea, its spine is very thick and sturdy. Its tail, which is shaped like a small fish, has eyes that light up.

name: Gorebyss
pokedex_description: A Gorebyss siphons the body fluids of prey through its thin, tubular mouth. Its light pink body color turns vivid when it finishes feeding.

name: Relicanth
pokedex_description: A Pokémon that was once believed to have been extinct. The species has not changed its form for 100 million years. It walks on the seafloor using its pectoral fins.

name: Luvdisc
pokedex_description: Luvdisc make the branches of Corsola their nests. There is a custom from long ago of giving a Luvdisc as a gift to express one's feelings of love.

name: Bagon
pokedex_description: Although it is small, this Pokémon is very powerful because its body is a bundle of muscles. It launches head-butts with its ironlike skull.

name: Shelgon
pokedex_description: It hardly eats while it awaits evolution. It becomes hardier by enduring hunger. Its shell peels off the instant it begins to evolve.

name: Salamence
pokedex_description: After many long years, its cellular structure underwent a sudden mutation to grow wings. When angered, it loses all thought and rampages out of control.

name: Beldum
pokedex_description: When Beldum gather in a swarm, they move in perfect unison as if they were but one Pokémon. They communicate with each other using brain waves.

name: Metang
pokedex_description: The claws tipping its arms pack the destructive power to tear through thick iron sheets as if they were silk. It flies at over 60 miles per hour.

name: Metagross
pokedex_description: Metagross has four brains that are joined by a complex neural network. As a result of integration, this Pokémon is smarter than a supercomputer.

name: Regirock
pokedex_description: A Pokémon that is made entirely of rocks and boulders. If parts of its body chip off in battle, Regirock repairs itself by adding new rocks.

name: Regice
pokedex_description: Its entire body is made of Antarctic ice. After extensive studies, researchers believe the ice was formed during an ice age.

name: Registeel
pokedex_description: Its body is harder than any other kind of metal. The body metal is composed of a mysterious substance. Not only is it hard, it shrinks and stretches flexibly.

name: Latias
pokedex_description: They make a small herd of only several members. They rarely make contact with people or other Pokémon. They disappear if they sense enemies.

name: Latios
pokedex_description: Even in hiding, it can detect the locations of others and sense their emotions since it has telepathy. Its intelligence allows it to understand human languages.

name: Kyogre
pokedex_description: Kyogre has appeared in mythology as the creator of the sea. After long years of feuding with Groudon, it took to sleep at the bottom of the sea.

name: Groudon
pokedex_description: Groudon has appeared in mythology as the creator of the land. It sleeps in magma underground and is said to make volcanoes erupt on awakening.

name: Rayquaza
pokedex_description: A Pokémon that flies endlessly in the ozone layer. It is said it would descend to the ground if Kyogre and Groudon were to fight.

name: Jirachi
pokedex_description: Jirachi is said to make wishes come true. While it sleeps, a tough crystalline shell envelops the body to protect it from enemies.

name: Deoxys
pokedex_description: A Pokémon that mutated from an extraterrestrial virus exposed to a laser beam. Its body is configured for superior agility and speed.

name: Turtwig
pokedex_description: Made from soil, the shell on its back hardens when it drinks water. It lives along lakes.

name: Grotle
pokedex_description: It lives along water in forests. In the daytime, it leaves the forest to sunbathe its treed shell.

name: Torterra
pokedex_description: Small Pokémon occasionally gather on its unmoving back to begin building their nests.

name: Chimchar
pokedex_description: It agilely scales sheer cliffs to live atop craggy mountains. Its fire is put out when it sleeps.

name: Monferno
pokedex_description: To intimidate attackers, it stretches the fire on its tail to make itself appear bigger.

name: Infernape
pokedex_description: It uses a special kind of martial arts involving all its limbs. Its fire never goes out.

name: Piplup
pokedex_description: Because it is very proud, it hates accepting food from people. Its thick down guards it from cold.

name: Prinplup
pokedex_description: It lives alone, away from others. Apparently, every one of them believes it is the most important.

name: Empoleon
pokedex_description: The three horns that extend from its beak attest to its power. The leader has the biggest horns.

name: Starly
pokedex_description: They flock in great numbers. Though small, they flap their wings with great power.

name: Staravia
pokedex_description: It flies around forests and fields in search of bug Pokémon. It stays within a huge flock.

name: Staraptor
pokedex_description: It has a savage nature. It will courageously challenge foes that are much larger.

name: Bidoof
pokedex_description: With nerves of steel, nothing can perturb it. It is more agile and active than it appears.

name: Bibarel
pokedex_description: It makes its nest by damming streams with bark and mud. It is known as an industrious worker.

name: Kricketot
pokedex_description: It shakes its head back to front, causing its antennae to hit each other and sound like a xylophone.

name: Kricketune
pokedex_description: It crosses its knifelike arms in front of its chest when it cries. It can compose melodies ad lib.

name: Shinx
pokedex_description: All of its fur dazzles if danger is sensed. It flees while the foe is momentarily blinded.

name: Luxio
pokedex_description: Its claws loose electricity with enough amperage to cause fainting. They live in small groups.

name: Luxray
pokedex_description: It has eyes that can see through anything. It spots and captures prey hiding behind objects.

name: Budew
pokedex_description: Over the winter, it closes its bud and endures the cold. In spring, the bud opens and releases pollen.

name: Roserade
pokedex_description: It attracts prey with a sweet aroma, then downs it with thorny whips hidden in its arms.

name: Cranidos
pokedex_description: It lived in jungles around 100 million years ago. Its skull is as hard as iron.

name: Rampardos
pokedex_description: Its powerful head butt has enough power to shatter even the most durable things upon impact.

name: Shieldon
pokedex_description: A Pokémon that lived in jungles around 100 million years ago. Its facial hide is extremely hard.

name: Bastiodon
pokedex_description: Any frontal attack is repulsed. It is a docile Pokémon that feeds on grass and berries.

name: Burmy
pokedex_description: To shelter itself from cold, wintry winds, it covers itself with a cloak made of twigs and leaves.

name: Wormadam
pokedex_description: When Burmy evolved, its cloak became a part of this Pokémon's body. The cloak is never shed.

name: Mothim
pokedex_description: It loves the honey of flowers and steals honey collected by Combee.

name: Combee
pokedex_description: A Pokémon formed by three others. It busily carries sweet floral honey to Vespiquen.

name: Vespiquen
pokedex_description: Its abdomen is a honeycomb for grubs. It raises its grubs on honey collected by Combee.

name: Pachirisu
pokedex_description: It makes fur balls that crackle with static electricity. It stores them with berries in tree holes.

name: Buizel
pokedex_description: It has a flotation sac that is like an inflatable collar. It floats on water with its head out.

name: Floatzel
pokedex_description: It floats using its well-developed flotation sac. It assists in the rescues of drowning people.

name: Cherubi
pokedex_description: The small ball holds the nutrients needed for evolution. Apparently, it is very sweet and tasty.

name: Cherrim
pokedex_description: It blooms during times of strong sunlight. It tries to make up for everything it endured as a bud.

name: Shellos
pokedex_description: Its colors and shapes differ from region to region. In the Sinnoh region, two types are confirmed.

name: Gastrodon
pokedex_description: It has a pliable body without any bones. If any part of its body is torn off, it grows right back.

name: Ambipom
pokedex_description: To eat, it deftly shucks nuts with its two tails. It rarely uses its arms now.

name: Drifloon
pokedex_description: A Pokémon formed by the spirits of people and Pokémon. It loves damp, humid seasons.

name: Drifblim
pokedex_description: It's drowzy in daytime, but flies off in the evening in big groups. No one knows where they go.

name: Buneary
pokedex_description: It slams foes by sharply uncoiling its rolled ears. It stings enough to make a grown-up cry in pain.

name: Lopunny
pokedex_description: An extremely cautious Pokémon. It cloaks its body with its fluffy ear fur when it senses danger.

name: Mismagius
pokedex_description: Its cries sound like incantations. Those hearing it are tormented by headaches and hallucinations.

name: Honchkrow
pokedex_description: Becoming active at night, it is known to swarm with numerous Murkrow in tow.

name: Glameow
pokedex_description: It claws if displeased and purrs when affectionate. Its fickleness is very popular among some.

name: Purugly
pokedex_description: It is a brazen brute that barges its way into another Pokémon's nest and claims it as its own.

name: Chingling
pokedex_description: It emits cries by agitating an orb at the back of its throat. It moves with flouncing hops.

name: Stunky
pokedex_description: It protects itself by spraying a noxious fluid from its rear. The stench lingers for 24 hours.

name: Skuntank
pokedex_description: It sprays a vile-smelling fluid from the tip of its tail to attack. Its range is over 160 feet.

name: Bronzor
pokedex_description: Implements shaped like it were discovered in ancient tombs. It is unknown if they are related.

name: Bronzong
pokedex_description: One caused a news sensation when it was dug up at a construction site after a 2,000-year sleep.

name: Bonsly
pokedex_description: It looks as if it is always crying. It is actually adjusting its body's fluid levels by eliminating excess.

name: Mime Jr.
pokedex_description: It habitually mimics foes. Once mimicked, the foe cannot take its eyes off this Pokémon.

name: Happiny
pokedex_description: It loves round white things. It carries an egg-shaped rock in imitation of Chansey.

name: Chatot
pokedex_description: It can learn and speak human words. If they gather, they all learn the same saying.

name: Spiritomb
pokedex_description: A Pokémon that was formed by 108 spirits. It is bound to a fissure in an odd keystone.

name: Gible
pokedex_description: It nests in small, horizontal holes in cave walls. It pounces to catch prey that stray too close.

name: Gabite
pokedex_description: There is a long-held belief that medicine made from its scales will heal even incurable illnesses.

name: Garchomp
pokedex_description: When it folds up its body and extends its wings, it looks like a jet plane. It flies at sonic speed.

name: Munchlax
pokedex_description: It wolfs down its weight in food once a day, swallowing food whole with almost no chewing.

name: Riolu
pokedex_description: The aura that emanates from its body intensifies to alert others if it is afraid or sad.

name: Lucario
pokedex_description: It has the ability to sense the auras of all things. It understands human speech.

name: Hippopotas
pokedex_description: It lives in arid places. Instead of perspiration, it expels grainy sand from its body.

name: Hippowdon
pokedex_description: It blasts internally stored sand from ports on its body to create a towering twister for attack.

name: Skorupi
pokedex_description: It grips prey with its tail claws and injects poison. It tenaciously hangs on until the poison takes.

name: Drapion
pokedex_description: It has the power in its clawed arms to make scrap of a car. The tips of its claws release poison.
